O.O. | $144,093.20 | Medium Spend |\n| 356 | Westbrook Advisers | $15,360.38 | Low Spend |\n| 357 | Wework Singapore Pte. Ltd. | $64,373.36 | Medium Spend |\n| 358 | Winmaxi Tours & Travels | $1,001.36 | Low Spend |\n| 359 | Wolt Enterprises Oy | $61.74 | Low Spend |\n| 360 | Work Easy Space Solutions Private Limited | $14,913.21 | Low Spend |\n| 361 | Workato, Inc. | $16,101.03 | Low Spend |\n| 362 | Xenon Savjetovanje D.O.O. | $164.02 | Low Spend |\n| 363 | Yellow Submarine D.O.O. | $486.21 | Low Spend |\n| 364 | Yoxel, Inc | $2,043.60 | Low Spend |\n| 365 | Zagrebacki Holding D.O.O. | $142.83 | Low Spend |\n| 366 | Zagrebtower D.O.O. | $183,754.42 | Medium Spend |\n| 367 | Zapier Inc. | $166.79 | Low Spend |\n| 368 | Zettanet | $183.37 | Low Spend |\n| 369 | Zivi Napitak D.O.O. | $3,699.58 | Low Spend |\n| 370 | Zuric I Partneri Odvjetnicko Drustvo D.O.O. | $24,135.44 | Low Spend |\n\n---\n\n### Key Summary\n\n- **Total vendors:** 386\n- **Total spend:** $7,887,360.40\n- **Spend populated:** all 386 rows have spend values\n- **Department column:** empty for all rows (not yet filled in)\n- **Description column:** empty for all rows (not yet filled in)\n- **Suggestion column:** empty for all rows (not yet filled in — this is where Consolidate/Terminate/Optimize values would go)\n- **Spend Category (DERIVED):** populated for all rows via formula — 360 Low, 21 Medium, 5 High\n- **Top vendor by far:** Salesforce Uk Ltd-Uk at $3,117,225.89 (39.5% of total spend)"}],"totalDurationMs":241837,"totalTokens":31093,"totalToolUseCount":11,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1682,"cache_read_input_tokens":18937,"output_tokens":10473,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1682},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01LWbeqUvGJwbiTkvqGtUAGm","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I have all the data. Now let me calculate the top 10 vendors by spend, their % of total spend, combined spend and concentration, and the counts for long-tail (<$50K) and high-spend strategic (≥$200K) vendors.\n\nTotal spend: $7,887,360.40\n\nTop vendors by spend (from the data):\n1. Salesforce Uk Ltd-Uk: $3,117,225.89\n2. Navan (Tripactions Inc): $357,983.62\n3. Bdo Llp: $343,081.39\n4. Tog Uk Properties Limited: $263,821.16\n\n\n5. Cloudcrossing Bvba: $208,675.15\n6. Zagrebtower D.O.O.: $183,754.42\n7. Innovent Spaces Private Limited: $147,347.80\n8. Weking D.O.O.: $144,093.20\n9. Jensten Insurance Brokers: $142,699.73\n10. Gpt Space & Co: $133,506.78\n\nNow I'm working through the percentage calculations for each vendor against the total spend. Now I'm adding up the top 10 spenders to see their combined total, working through the cumulative sum step by step.\n\nThe top 10 vendors together account for $5,042,189.14, which represents 63.93% of the total spend. Now I need to segment the remaining vendors by spend level—identifying which ones fall below $50K and which ones are strategic partners spending $200K or more.\n\nLooking at the high-spend tier, I can see Salesforce leads at $3.1M, followed by Navan, BDO LLP, TOG UK Properties, and Cloudcrossing BVBA all above the $200K threshold. That gives me 5 vendors in the strategic high-spend category, though I should verify whether the sheet's own categorization uses a different threshold than $200K. Looking at the medium spend vendors more carefully, I see the threshold isn't strictly $50K—some are above it like Amazon Web Services at $106K and Aetna at $124K, while others like Workato are below at $16K. I need to manually count vendors from the data that fall specifically under $50K to identify the true long-tail segment. Looking at the rest of the vendor list, I notice a couple of \"Medium\" spend vendors actually fall below the $50K threshold—HubSpot Ireland Limited and Workato, Inc.—which would classify them as long-tail. Checking the \"Low Spend\" category, all 360 vendors appear to be below $50K as expected, with the highest being Dcirrus Limited at just $56.\n\n5K. Wait, that's actually above $50K but still labeled as Low Spend, and I'm seeing several others in that category—Baringa Partners, CBRE, Microsoft Ireland Operations, Fluency Digital, Rimini Street UK—all with spend between $50K and $56K. So the sheet's categorization doesn't align cleanly with a strict $50K threshold. I need to recount vendors with spend strictly below $50K, excluding those Low Spend entries that exceed that amount.\n\nLooking more carefully at the actual numbers, I'm finding vendors like Arges HR at $48K, Cognizant Technology Solutions at $47K, and Columbus Consulting at $48K that genuinely fall below $50K, while Ernst & Young Advisory is right at the edge with $49,590.63. I need to correct my count—Hubspot and Workato are actually below $50K, so that brings the total vendors under $50K to 356. Now I'm looking at which vendors hit the $200K threshold, starting with Salesforce at over $3.1M and checking others in that range. Looking at the Low Spend vendors more carefully, I can identify 6 that fall above the $50K threshold—Dcirrus, Baringa Partners, Microsoft Ireland Operations, Fluency Digital, Rimini Street UK, and Cbre. From the Medium Spend category, there's at least one vendor below $50K, like Hubspot Ireland Limited at $32,187.\n\n41, plus Workato at $16,101.03, giving me 2 total. So the long-tail count under $50K works out to 356 vendors when I subtract the 6 from Low Spend and add back the 2 from Medium Spend.\n\nNow I'm identifying the top 10 vendors by total spend, starting with Salesforce at $3.1 million, followed by Navan and BDO. I've confirmed the top 10 vendors, with the combined spend totaling just over $5 million, which represents about 64% of the total budget. Now I'm updating my records with these findings.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":10768,"cache_read_input_tokens":15979,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":10768,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"34892ac9-88c1-4dab-a8af-d52812e99525","uuid":"1b085072-a7e0-499a-9cb5-79178dbf64b8"}
